      "content": "hey, im working on this script for a dark comedy that satirizes how movies treat different ethnicities. i want to make sure i dont accidentally fall into the same old traps, or maybe i can use them ironically to make a point. can u list out like 5 common racial stereotypes that hollywood uses way too much? just so i know what they are and can avoid/subvert them.",
